data.description: Don't miss out on this lovely northwest Fresno home. This 4-bedroom home features tile flooring downstairs along with granite countertops and stainless-steel appliances in the kitchen. All of the bedrooms are located upstairs. The large main bedroom features a walk-in closet along with a large main bathroom. In addition, the home will have a paid off solar system for the new buyer's convenience. This gated community also features a community pool and clubhouse for your enjoyment.
